## **Installation & Usage Guide**  

### **Install Dependencies**  
Run the following command to install required libraries:  
bash
```
pip install -r requirements.txt

```

---

 How It Works

When you run Veilgen, an interactive menu will appear, allowing you to choose the type of data to generate:
````
â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”
â”‚            Choose an Option          â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¤
â”‚  1    â”‚ Generate Passwords            â”‚
â”‚  2    â”‚ Generate Emails               â”‚
â”‚  3    â”‚ Generate Usernames            â”‚
â”‚  4    â”‚ Generate Aliases              â”‚
â”‚  5    â”‚ Generate Phone Numbers        â”‚
â”‚  6    â”‚ Generate IPs                  â”‚
â”‚  7    â”‚ Generate Credit Cards         â”‚
â”‚  8    â”‚ Generate IMEI Numbers         â”‚
â”‚  9    â”‚ Generate Fake Identity        â”‚
â”‚ 10    â”‚ Generate User Agents          â”‚
â”‚ 11    â”‚ Generate GPS Coordinates      â”‚
â”‚ 12    â”‚ Generate MAC Addresses        â”‚
â”‚ 13    â”‚ Generate Birthdates           â”‚
â”‚ 14    â”‚ Generate National ID (SSN)    â”‚
â”‚ 15    â”‚ Generate Addresses            â”‚
â”‚ 99    â”‚ Decrypt and Show Data         â”‚
â”‚  0    â”‚ Exit                          â”‚
â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”´â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
````
 Enter a number to choose an option.
 Specify how many records you want to generate.
 Data is automatically encrypted and saved as a .enc file.
 Use option 99 to decrypt and view saved data.


